review_text: The fields aren't well maintained. With netting buried in the dirt that's now coming to the surface. Playing any sports or running on the grass has become hazardous.

Hey what can I say ? If you are a dog lover, need and enjoy a space to have fun with your pooch, this is it. Children's play area, work out features for the health conscious and in general terms a fun and popular place in the local neighborhood. Folks need green areas like as an alternative to the grey metropolitan backdrop of big city existance. Best to utilize the facilities throughout the day to avoid potential antisocial activities at other times.
